  How to run FornaC
  -----------------

  1. Clone the repository: https://github.com/Dimitar-92/galaxytools.git
  2. Copy the folder "fornac" from this repository and paste it in the local instance of your galaxy (Folder structure: galaxy > tools > fornac)
  3. Go to galaxy > config and open tool_config.xml
  4. paste 
        <section id="fornac" name="fornac">
        <tool file="fornac/fornac.xml" />
        </section>
     in the tool_config.xml file
  5. open terminal and go to galaxy > tools > fornac and run the following commands:
      - sudo npm install jsdom@9.12.0
      - sudo npm install svg2png@4.1.1
  6. Once the installation is done, run the galaxy using sh run.sh command and fornac should be visible on the left hand side of the screen
  7. Test input file can be found in the galaxy > tools > fornac > test-data folder

  How to run the AntaRNA - FornaC Workflow
  ----------------------------------------

  1. Run the local instance of galaxy from terminal
  2. Install AntaRNA from toolshed
  3. Click on workflows on the top menu on the screen
  4. Click on "upload or import workflow" tab at the top right corner of the screen
  5. Browse the file "Galaxy-Workflow-AntaRNA_-_FornaC.ga" provided in the fornac_documentation folder and select import 